Class LegacyCustomerAdapter

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.percyvega.motionpoint.LegacyCustomerAdapter
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    LegacyCustomer, java.io.Serializable

    public class LegacyCustomerAdapter
extends java.lang.Object
implements LegacyCustomer
    LegacyCustomerAdapter implements the Adapter Design Pattern to provide the bridge between the CRM implementations and the Legacy CRM implementations.
